      "description": "CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against published FDA experimental measurements for the generic centrifugal pump across five flow-speed operating points. Mean absolute relative error of 8.3% observed; all predictions fall within experimental uncertainty bands. RH < 1 criterion satisfied at all conditions.",
